# Formatting & Quality

## Best Practices
- Use Prettier as the source of truth for code formatting (including prettier-plugin-tailwindcss)
- Follow ESLint rules for:
  - React hooks
  - Import ordering
  - TanStack Query
- Enable strict TypeScript settings:
  - noImplicitAny
  - strictNullChecks
  - exactOptionalPropertyTypes

## Avoid
- Using PropTypes in TypeScript files
- Overriding Prettier's default semicolon rules with Standard.js rules
